      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The city treasury was enriched\nto the extent of $50 yesterday aft.\nernoon by the forfeiture of bonds\nby persons charged with vagrancy\n\"Vags\" are becoming somewhat\nscarce on the police court docket\nsince the police have turned their\nattentions on the |. w. w. fight.\nEverything has been \"disorderly\nconduct\"-d. c. for Shorthand\nthere have been but few bonds to\nforfeit."
